{"lastModified":1775541936027,"uri":"c::7646090758::vessel::d5cbd3a4-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nThe 22.33 m motor yacht Prewi, built by Azimut in 2022, offers stylish interiors by Achille Salvagni Architetti and accommodates up to 8 guests in 4 luxurious cabins. With a cruising speed of 21 knots and a shallow draft of just 1.75 m, she is perfect for exploring secluded bays and coastal waters. Onboard comfort is enhanced by Wi-Fi, air conditioning, and a professional crew of 3 ensuring a relaxed charter experience. Available year-round in the Mediterranean, Prewi is the ideal yacht for family-friendly adventures and unforgettable escapes.","blueprint":{"name":"PREWI","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbd3a4-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::311de520-818d-11f0-b258-557c5c98d413/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbd3a4-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::3107ec20-818d-11f0-9f7a-ab10d1eb8b4b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbd3a4-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::310e7bd0-818d-11f0-b256-557c5c98d413/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbd3a4-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::310f6630-818d-11f0-a7ab-57e8a689a8e2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbd3a4-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::3113fa10-818d-11f0-b258-557c5c98d413/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbd3a4-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::3120cb50-818d-11f0-9de5-197ba7697586/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbd3a4-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::3122c720-818d-11f0-b258-557c5c98d413/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbd3a4-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::31122550-818d-11f0-b256-557c5c98d413/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbd3a4-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::311336c0-818d-11f0-b257-557c5c98d413/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbd3a4-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4